\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Disturbance deviation is ~0.07\'b0, not ~1.3\'b0.
\f0 \'a0The specified gains reject the 0.12 N\'b7m / 50 ms pulse almost completely (the D term counters within 1-2 control cycles). The two curves overlap at full scale, so I added a deviation inset to fig04 to make the response visible. The old 1.3\'b0 figure likely came from the buggy wind moment arm noted in CLAUDE.md.\cb1 \
