\f0 \'a0The 300 deg/s servo slew limit is marginal against the loop bandwidth at peak thrust (33 N), so the gimbal chatters before calming as thrust drops. This is a genuine consequence of the specified actuator model, and arguably a publishable finding about actuator sizing.\cb1 \
